{"tid":2324429,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：奧燒好易教啫！","createTime":"2020-12-14T02:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T04:12:28.000Z","uid":31314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a318483bb7a5ae3f2bfeab2a49f27563d2ec6cd","tid":2324429,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"傳奇領隊雲加力撐攻中奧斯爾，認為阿仙奴主帥阿迪達認為重用這名前德國國腳，更指他根據不難教。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯爾（Mesut Ozil）不獲阿迪達重用，而且沒有被列入英超、歐霸盃的大軍名單。雲加（Arsene Wenger）說：「他是藝術家，很敏感，需要支持和一個能促使他們全力以赴的環境。」 雲加在離開兵工廠前，與奧斯爾續約，令對方享有全隊最高的35萬鎊周薪，「奧斯爾並不難教。他是一個很有創造力的球員，需要在場上找到樂趣。」 阿仙奴在沒有奧燒之下，今季火力極差，11場英超只取得10球，僅比榜尾3弱多。71歲的雲加表示：「球隊需要有一位更有創造力的球員，他可以做比較少防守工作，但你要在他周圍建立一個能夠彌補這些不足的團隊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/VastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FVastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif&h=7a584c55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf1dc22f77208463c14289748525c140c2de8ba","tid":2324429,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"Arsene <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b236f37c4bce64b75cf42ee7c043362542627","tid":2324429,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebf1dc22f77208463c14289748525c140c2de8ba","tid":2324429,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"Arsene <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"成班不孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /